# {{PROJECT_NAME}} Common Docs Entrypoint

This is the lightweight entrypoint for the {{PROJECT_NAME}} shared knowledge base. Acting as the {{ROLE_TERM}}, read this file first, summarize the current state, then pull only the task-relevant documents on demand. Do not linearly read every file at startup.

Documentation language policy:

- Docs under `docs/` are maintained in {{DOCS_LANG}}. Code identifiers, file paths, commands, and metric names stay verbatim in their original form; never translate them.
- Claude Chat replies to {{USER_NAME}} are written in {{CHAT_LANG}}, unless {{USER_NAME}} explicitly asks otherwise.
- Claude Code prompts may be written in {{CODE_LANG}}, but they must preserve the path and operational constraints below.

