### 5.3 File Lifecycle

Creating, deleting, or renaming a doc means: update the nearest directory README or router, update this file map and cascade, fix every reference with rg, and run `make docs-check`. The guard in `scripts/check_docs_consistency.py` enforces required files, routers, links, and the two byte-identical mirror blocks. Docs are language-agnostic (Unicode); there is no character/script policy.

