## 7. Update Discipline

- When code or runner status changes, sync `docs/entrypoint.md`, `docs/project/project-status.md`, and `docs/operations/session-kickoff.md` first, then cascade to method docs if needed.
- New operational constraints go into `docs/operations/rules/operational-constraints.md`; new forbidden actions into `docs/operations/rules/forbidden-actions.md`; new terms into `docs/concepts/glossary.md`.
- Project Instructions changes are provided as text for {{USER_NAME}} to paste; the {{ROLE_TERM}} never edits them silently.
- After docs edits, run `make docs-check` and fix all failures before the final response.
